{"tid":814642,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"UEFA或增設第3個歐洲賽","createTime":"2018-09-11T11:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T13:12:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4723dd8acad1610709767e8d5a013167cfecc984","tid":814642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=FMEASu643V7aAMZ1LAlKwY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=9b555c3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】歐洲足協（UEFA）計劃從2021/22年球季開始，舉辦第3個歐洲賽，這計劃正等待執行委員會的最終批准。<br />\n<br />\n新辦的歐洲賽將會加入歐聯和歐霸盃，令到參與歐洲足球比賽的球隊，總數增加到96隊。祖雲達斯會長兼歐洲球會協會主席艾格尼（Andrea Agnelli）說，「UEFA剛宣佈的這些新規則，比我們現有的更有效，將會帶來令人驚訝的效果。」<br />\n<br />\n「計劃有待UEFA的執行委員會批准，引入第3個歐洲賽已開綠燈，去到2021/22球季，參加球隊總數會達到96支。」艾格尼補充。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，歐聯不太可能被改變，而歐霸盃或將改革以提升質素，參與歐霸盃的球隊將由目前的48支球隊下降至32支，球隊來自世界排名較低的國家將改為參與新的比賽。"},{"pid":"4d712d2a1b477f7103c67333bdca091d321fcf3c","tid":814642,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:27:29.000Z","msg":"歐洲聯賽弱者盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c9289647481e9e8155e1a6e3bfd4352c5f12b7","tid":814642,"uid":30476,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"然左可以打皇者曼？"},{"pid":"4aed6846cabb2a9d21a0e550f5105744c4b8efb7","tid":814642,"uid":6003,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"即係以前圖圖盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a5944dd6d265a1aa3aa0f748f9132662b92291","tid":814642,"uid":8515,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"應該搵每個聯賽降班果3隊參賽"},{"pid":"f9fff78cd082cfaebfece743166112afb1e7de5a","tid":814642,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51a5944dd6d265a1aa3aa0f748f9132662b92291","tid":814642,"uid":8515,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018